headline: CF Industries Stock Shows Healthy Growth; Earns Membership In 95-Plus Composite Rating Club
summary: Fertilizer is a growth industry, in every sense of the word.  Shares of No. 1 ranked fertilizer maker CF Industries gapped up 6.5% Friday and at one point early Monday they were up another 4.5% before pulling back for a nearly 1% gain.  Also on Monday, the IBD SmartSelect Composite Rating for CF Industries stock rose from 94 to a near-best 96.

headline: CF (CF) Soars 6.5%: Is Further Upside Left in the Stock?
summary: CF (CF) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
